data.description: Just listed in Sterling Lake in the City Limits of Jefferson!  This 5 bedroom/3.5 bath home sits on a large corner lot and is well landscaped with a large fenced in back yard.  The open concept main living space is perfect for entertaining.  The kitchen offers white cabinets with a spacious kitchen island and granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and beautiful hardwood floors.  The expansive owners suite is located on the main level and has high vaulted ceilings with a large on-suite bath and walk in closet.  Upstairs you will find 4 additional bedrooms with 2 more full baths and a large loft.    Perfect for a media room or additional playroom space.  This gated community offers a community pool, side walks, street lights, and is close proximity to schools and downtown Jefferson!
